{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br> You experience the surreal nightmare of an insect. A squirrel tries to fly. An alligator is going through an existential crisis. A bridge made of flesh is broken. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This bridge eats squirrel\u2019s parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/BridgeEat_2.gif?t=1728940521\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This surreal universe can turn out disturbingly relatable. It\u2019s a dark existential experience that can be interpreted in many ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/reality_450_en.gif?t=1728940521\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a praying mantis, you explore an eerie world, meet animals, collect dreams, and make impactful decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Playtime of about 1h</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Exploration game with casual mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Interactive story with 2 different endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Disturbing, violent, and poetic story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Meet depressing squirrels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Play as a praying mantis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What players say : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- <i>\u201cit's so aesthetically and tonally unsettling\u201d</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- <i>\u201cWhen the credits roll you will be thinking about the game, and yourself, and if you should have done it differently\u201d</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- <i>\u201cIt's a unique, creative, and well done dive into a mind in crisis\u201d</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The end of hope","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap